  "description": {
    "zh": "有时候你得为近距离CQB作战做好准备，你不能指望人们永远保持距离和你在舒适范围内作战。有时你的敌人想方设法的接近你，然后轻松的把你干掉……或者……你去接近他们，打一个先手。听起来如何？很有道理对吧？\n\n好吧，那就用冲锋枪做一些训练，证明你能用冲锋枪在短距离内干掉敌人。祝你好运，士兵。",
    "en": "Sometimes you gotta prepare for close encounters, you can't rely on people keeping their distance and making themselves an easy target. Sometimes your enemy will get close to you, and take you out easily... Or.. You are the one who gets close, and take your enemy out easily first. How does that sound, makes sense right?\nAlright then, get some training with SMGs then, and prove that you manage to take out people from a short distance with SMGs. Good luck out there warrior."
  },
